high_descs: Turn right, proceed to table.  Turn right, proceed to refrigerator.  Turn left, proceed to table, turn left to face table.
Pick up the front tomato, closest to the plate and left salt shaker.
Turn left, proceed across room to far counter.
Open cabinet directly ahead, under the pepper shaker.  Put tomato in the pan located on the shelf.
Pick up pot with tomato in it.
Turn left to face coffee maker.
Place pan with tomato on counter, directly left of coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Move tomato from table to pan, put both on a counter.

high_descs: move right towards the table
pick up a tomato from the table
move left to the shelf
drop  the tomato in the plate in the shelf
pick up the plate from the shelf
turn left and head to the table
place the plate on the table
anns.task_desc: place a plate with a tomato in it on the table

high_descs: Turn and cross the room, turn right again just before the kitchen table, and move around it so you're standing on the side closest to the fridge, but facing the table.
Pick up the tomato closest to you from the table.
Turn around and carry the tomato past the kitchen sink to the counter space on the opposite side of the room where the microwave is.
Open the cupboard beneath the pepper grinder on the counter, and place the tomato on the gray plate inside.
Pick up the plate with the tomato on it from the cupboard.
Turn to your left to face the coffee maker.
Place the plate with the tomato on top on the counter above the dishwasher and left of the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Move a tomato on a plate to the counter by the coffee maker.
